						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Turkey-launches-new-Africa-program" title="Turkey launches new Africa program" alt="link">Turkey launches new Africa program</a></h2>

	
					<p>A Turkish minister has announced that Turkey is launching a new development assistance program for African countries. The aim of the program is to improve relations between Turkey and Africa, to provide African countries with modern agriculture and animal breeding techniques, to raise qualified experts, and raise incomes and living standards,’ State Minister Said Yazicioglu said on Friday, during a promotional meeting for the Africa Agricultural Development Program (Source: Today’s Zaman, 2 August 2008).</p>
							<p><span class="date">8/09/2008</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
