						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Investment-in-agricultural-research-key-to-solving-food-crisis" title="Investment in agricultural research key to solving food crisis " alt="link">Investment in agricultural research key to solving food crisis </a></h2>

	
					<p>Investing in agricultural research and development is key to attainment of short and long-term goals for most governments and it is imperative that the agricultural sector ministries do so for meaningful redress of food security and poor livelihoods, Director of Kenya’s Agricultural Research Institute, KARI has said. According to Dr Ephraim A. Mukisira, although agricultural research contributes significantly to technology development leading to increased productivity, the sector continues to receive miniscule funding from the central government (Source: Henry Neondo, African Science News Service, 25 July 2008).</p>
							<p><span class="date">8/09/2008</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Investment-in-agricultural-research-key-to-solving-food-crisis">Read more...</a>
</div>
